        "id": 8023114154175,
        "title": "ARMOUR G Series Drip Tip",
        "handle": "armour-g-series-drip-tip",
        "body_html": "<h1 class=\"Polaris-Header-Title_2qj8j\">VAPORESSO ARMOUR G Series Drip Tip</h1>\n<h2><strong>Features:</strong></h2>\n<p>TThe ARMOUR G series drip tip is designed with precision and durability in mind. It's made with high-quality materials that will withstand daily use and provide a comfortable vaping experience. It has two types of drip tip. One is DTL and another one is MTL.</p>\n<h2><strong>Physical Parameter:</strong></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Fit for: VAPORESSO ARMOUR G Series Drip Tip</li>\n<li>Quantity:2pcs/pack</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>\n<br><strong>Packing list:</strong><br>\n</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>2 x ARMOUR G series drip tip</li>\n</ul>",
