        "id": 6814704468016,
        "title": "Forever Mon Amour - Mini Nail Stickers",
        "handle": "forever-mon-amour-mini-nail-stickers",
        "body_html": "<p>Mini nail stickers with pink and red hearts, roses, trendy abstract faces &amp; more to create nail art made with love.</p>\n<p>Bring the love to your gel manicure with our Forever Mon Amour mini nail stickers! Cute pink and red heart designs, rose outlines, paper planes, \u201cbisou\u201d script and face line drawings to choose from!</p>\n<p>Keep it simple with a heart sticker on an accent nail, be trendy with the abstract face drawing stickers, or mix and match them all for a heart-stopping look you\u2019ll love.</p>",
