      "product": {
        "id": 8492561105032,
        "title": "Compostable Coffee Pods for Keurig\u00ae Machines -  Sample Pod",
        "handle": "love-grown-compostable-coffee-pods-for-keurig-machines-sample-pod",
        "body_html": "<p>What's <em>out</em> in 2025? plastic-y coffee pods with too little coffee to brew a good cup. What's <em>in</em> in 2025? Plastic-free, fully compostable pods with 40% more coffee that's single origin, responsibly farmed and roasted using a process that maximizes flavor and purity. Try a pod or two or\u00a0<a href=\"https://hivebrands.com/products/love-grown-compostable-coffee-pods\">buy 'em by the box</a>.</p>",
        "published_at": "2025-02-25T16:06:56-05:00",
