    "https://vv6kxd-np.myshopify.com": {
      "product": {
        "id": 10062882046226,
        "title": "For Linda Gluten Free Pumpkin Bread Mix",
        "handle": "for-linda-gluten-free-pumpkin-bread-mix",
        "body_html": "Linda Gluten Free Pumpkin Bread Mix  <p>Linda Gluten Free Pumpkin Bread Mix is a premium flavor concentrate designed for commercial food manufacturers, R&amp;D teams, and culinary professionals seeking to infuse their creations with the rich, warm taste of pumpkin. This concentrate captures the essence of pumpkin, offering a balanced blend of sweetness and spice that is ideal for a variety of food applications. It is used to impart a consistent and authentic pumpkin flavor in products, ensuring that each batch delivers the same delightful taste experience.</p>  <strong>Applications:</strong> <p>This flavor concentrate is typically used in a wide range of baked goods, including breads, muffins, and cakes, where a robust pumpkin flavor is desired. It is also suitable for use in beverages such as lattes and smoothies, as well as in sauces and dressings that benefit from a hint of pumpkin spice. The concentrate's versatility makes it an excellent choice for seasonal products and limited-time offerings.</p>  <strong>Benefit:</strong> <p>Using Linda Gluten Free Pumpkin Bread Mix offers several functional and business benefits. It ensures flavor consistency across large production batches, reducing the variability that can occur with fresh ingredients. This concentrate is cost-efficient, allowing manufacturers to achieve the desired flavor profile without the expense of fresh pumpkin. Additionally, it supports clean-label initiatives by providing a natural flavor solution that aligns with consumer demand for transparency and simplicity in ingredient lists.</p>  <strong>Versatility:</strong> <p>The concentrate's potency allows for flexible flavor control, enabling culinary professionals to adjust the intensity of the pumpkin flavor to suit different product formulations. This versatility supports product innovation, allowing for the creation of unique and differentiated offerings in the marketplace. A small amount of concentrate goes a long way, making it an economical choice for large-scale production.</p>  <strong>Quality Assurance:</strong> <p>Linda Gluten Free Pumpkin Bread Mix is manufactured under strict quality control standards to ensure safety and consistency. Each batch undergoes rigorous testing to verify its flavor profile and potency, ensuring that it meets the high standards expected by commercial food manufacturers. The production process adheres to industry best practices, guaranteeing a reliable and high-quality product.</p>  <strong>Sustainability:</strong> <p>The concentrate is produced with a commitment to environmentally responsible sourcing and manufacturing practices. Ingredients are sourced from suppliers who prioritize sustainability, and the production process is designed to minimize waste and reduce environmental impact. This aligns with the growing trend towards sustainable ingredient solutions in the food industry.</p>  <strong>Storage:</strong> <p>To maintain the freshness and potency of Linda Gluten Free Pumpkin Bread Mix, it should be stored in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight. Once opened, the concentrate should be tightly sealed and used within the recommended timeframe to ensure optimal flavor quality. Proper storage will help preserve the concentrate's integrity and extend its shelf life.</p>",
        "published_at": "2025-10-10T08:24:41-07:00",
        "created_at": "2025-02-28T01:21:15-08:00",
        "updated_at": "2026-04-02T10:59:45-07:00",
