        "title": "United Kingdom & Ireland eSIM",
        "handle": "united-kingdom-uk-ireland-esim",
        "body_html": "<p>Travel across the UK and Ireland with one eSIM from the moment you arrive. Whether you're exploring London or Dublin, this two-country combo eSIM is your ideal travel companion, keeping you connected with no need to switch eSIM plans or unexpected roaming charges.</p>\n<div class=\"product__description rte quick-add-hidden\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<strong>Flexible Options:</strong><span>\u00a0</span>Choose from a range of data plans designed to suit your travel needs, up to 180 days with 50GB of data</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Instant Activation:</strong><span>\u00a0</span>Your plan begins the moment you touchdown in the United Kingdom or Ireland</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Simple Setup:</strong><span>\u00a0</span>Your eSim will instantly be sent by email,<span>\u00a0</span>No ID registration required<br>\n</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Effortless Monitoring:<span>\u00a0</span></strong>Track your data usage online for peace of mind</li>\n<li>\n<span><strong>Change of mind:</strong>\u00a0We\u2019ve got you covered with a 7-day return policy on any unused eSIM plans</span><meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>",
