        "body_html": "<p>Wholesale eraser wedges for back to school students of all ages in elementary, middle and high school. Our pink erasers come in a wholesale case with 96 erasers.</p>\n<p>With bulk discount pricing, these erasers are a great item for charity donations.</p>\n<p><b><span style=\"font-family: 'Segoe UI',sans-serif; color: #002868;\">FEATURES</span></b><br>\u2022 ERASER WEDGE<br>\u2022 NON TOXIC<br>\u2022 FOR AGES 8 AND UP<br>\u2022 IDEAL FOR OFFICE AND SCHOOL</p>\n<p><b><span style=\"font-family: 'Segoe UI',sans-serif; color: #002868;\">SPECIFICATIONS</span></b><br><strong>Colors in Assortment:</strong> Pink<br><strong>Case Pack Quantity:</strong> 96 <br><strong>Material:</strong> Rubber <br><strong>Item Weight:</strong> 0.25 oz <br><strong>Item Dimensions:</strong> 2\" x 1\" x .5\"<br><strong>Case Weight:</strong> 4 lbs<br><strong>Case Dimensions:</strong> 14\" x 10\" x 4\"</p>",
