        "id": 8119699013706,
        "title": "Red Glitter Acrylic Top End Barbell Tongue Ring",
        "handle": "red-glitter-acrylic-barbell-tongue-ring",
        "body_html": "<h5>Product Details</h5>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong><u>Red Glitter Acrylic Top End Barbell Tongue Ring</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Give your every word some extra impact with this 14 gauge tongue jewelry. It's made with a 5/8 inch 316L surgical grade stainless steel straight barbell. It features a bar-shaped top end made clear acrylic with red glitter set inside and a matching ball end on the bottom. Let your tongue piercing brighten things up with this glitzy glitter tongue piercing ring.</span></p>\n<h5><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Specifications</span></h5>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">14 Gauge (1.6mm), 5/8\" (16mm), 316L Surgical Grade Stainless Steel Straight Barbell, Acrylic Ends</span></p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>",
