    "https://desert-noir.myshopify.com": {
      "product": {
        "id": 6642174951586,
        "title": "Cactus Cutting \u2013 Center Cut Cactus Live Succulent, Cacti Cutting Propagation, Rare Desert Plant",
        "handle": "center-cut-cactus-various",
        "body_html": "<h2 data-start=\"343\" data-end=\"367\">\ud83c\udf31 Product Overview</h2>\n<p data-start=\"368\" data-end=\"639\">This <strong data-start=\"373\" data-end=\"394\">Center Cut Cactus</strong> is a carefully selected live succulent cutting\u2014perfect for propagation or adding unique desert flair to your collection. Whether you're starting a new plant or expanding your garden, this cutting offers an easy and rewarding growth opportunity.</p>\n<hr data-start=\"641\" data-end=\"644\">\n<h2 data-start=\"646\" data-end=\"666\">\ud83c\udf43 Key Features</h2>\n<ul data-start=\"667\" data-end=\"1058\">\n<li data-start=\"667\" data-end=\"763\">\n<p data-start=\"669\" data-end=\"763\"><strong data-start=\"669\" data-end=\"685\">Live Cutting</strong>: Freshly cut and allowed to callus, ready for rooting or immediate planting</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"764\" data-end=\"856\">\n<p data-start=\"766\" data-end=\"856\"><strong data-start=\"766\" data-end=\"787\">Propagation Ideal</strong>: Formed with healthy areoles to ensure successful root development</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"857\" data-end=\"959\">\n<p data-start=\"859\" data-end=\"959\"><strong data-start=\"859\" data-end=\"878\">Low Maintenance</strong>: Thrives in bright light and dry conditions; ideal for both beginners and pros</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"960\" data-end=\"1058\">\n<p data-start=\"962\" data-end=\"1058\"><strong data-start=\"962\" data-end=\"979\">Versatile Use</strong>: Perfect for pots, terrariums, garden beds, or as part of a cutting collection</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"1060\" data-end=\"1063\">\n<h2 data-start=\"1065\" data-end=\"1096\">\ud83c\udf35 Why Buy from DesertNoir</h2>\n<ul data-start=\"1097\" data-end=\"1386\">\n<li data-start=\"1097\" data-end=\"1163\">\n<p data-start=\"1099\" data-end=\"1163\"><strong data-start=\"1099\" data-end=\"1116\">Arizona-grown</strong> stock, prepped under full sun for resilience</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1164\" data-end=\"1232\">\n<p data-start=\"1166\" data-end=\"1232\"><strong data-start=\"1166\" data-end=\"1188\">Bare-root shipping</strong> minimizes transplant stress and packaging</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1233\" data-end=\"1307\">\n<p data-start=\"1235\" data-end=\"1307\">Trusted <strong data-start=\"1243\" data-end=\"1258\">Star Seller</strong> service\u2014quick fulfillment and careful handling</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1308\" data-end=\"1386\">\n<p data-start=\"1310\" data-end=\"1386\">Ideal for propagators, collectors, or anyone seeking a unique cactus starter</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"1388\" data-end=\"1391\">\n<h2 data-start=\"1393\" data-end=\"1420\">\ud83c\udf3f Care &amp; Growing Tips</h2>\n<ul data-start=\"1421\" data-end=\"1889\">\n<li data-start=\"1421\" data-end=\"1514\">\n<p data-start=\"1423\" data-end=\"1514\"><strong data-start=\"1423\" data-end=\"1441\">Hardiness Zone</strong>: USDA <strong data-start=\"1448\" data-end=\"1462\">Zone 9b\u201311</strong> (safe outdoors when kept dry, protect below 35\u00b0F)</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1515\" data-end=\"1593\">\n<p data-start=\"1517\" data-end=\"1593\"><strong data-start=\"1517\" data-end=\"1526\">Light</strong>: Provide full sun to bright indirect light to prevent elongation</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1594\" data-end=\"1697\">\n<p data-start=\"1596\" data-end=\"1697\"><strong data-start=\"1596\" data-end=\"1605\">Water</strong>: After planting and rooting, use a soak-and-dry schedule\u2014water only when soil fully dries</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1698\" data-end=\"1778\">\n<p data-start=\"1700\" data-end=\"1778\"><strong data-start=\"1700\" data-end=\"1708\">Soil</strong>: Use a fast-draining cactus or succulent mix (with perlite or grit)</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1779\" data-end=\"1889\">\n<p data-start=\"1781\" data-end=\"1889\"><strong data-start=\"1781\" data-end=\"1800\">Propagation Tip</strong>: Allow cutting to callus for 3\u20137 days before planting; root development visible in weeks</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"1891\" data-end=\"1894\">\n<h2 data-start=\"1896\" data-end=\"1924\">\ud83d\udce6 Shipping &amp; Guarantee</h2>\n<ul data-start=\"1925\" data-end=\"2322\">\n<li data-start=\"1925\" data-end=\"2008\">\n<p data-start=\"1927\" data-end=\"2008\">Shipped <strong data-start=\"1935\" data-end=\"1948\">bare-root</strong> every <strong data-start=\"1955\" data-end=\"1968\">Wednesday</strong> for orders placed by the prior Sunday</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"2009\" data-end=\"2093\">\n<p data-start=\"2011\" data-end=\"2093\">Ships within <strong data-start=\"2024\" data-end=\"2045\">3\u20137 business days</strong>, with possible slight delays due to inventory</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"2094\" data-end=\"2161\">\n<p data-start=\"2096\" data-end=\"2161\">Each cutting is unique\u2014photos showcase typical quality and size</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"2162\" data-end=\"2249\">\n<p data-start=\"2164\" data-end=\"2249\">Contact us within 48 hours of arrival for any issues\u2014we\u2019ll assist with replacements</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"2250\" data-end=\"2322\">\n<p data-start=\"2252\" data-end=\"2322\">International buyers: responsible for customs, duties, and regulations</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"2324\" data-end=\"2327\">\n<h2 data-start=\"2329\" data-end=\"2348\">\u2728 Why It Rocks</h2>\n<p data-start=\"2349\" data-end=\"2562\">A fresh <strong data-start=\"2357\" data-end=\"2378\">Center Cut Cactus</strong> gives you the excitement of growing from the ground up. With strong propagation potential and desert-hardened vigor, it\u2019s a rewarding and sculptural addition to any cactus collection.</p>",
        "published_at": "2025-06-14T22:30:07-07:00",
        "created_at": "2021-03-28T11:02:41-07:00",
