    "https://jenteal-soaps.myshopify.com": {
      "product": {
        "id": 5324846825634,
        "title": "Handmade Soaps - Unwrapped - 3.5 - 4.5 oz.",
        "handle": "handmade-soaps-unwrapped-3-5-4-5-oz",
        "body_html": "<div>\n<span></span><br>\n</div>\n<div>\n<span></span><br>\n</div>\n<div>\n<span></span><span><span></span></span>\n<h1><span>Handmade Soaps - Unwrapped</span></h1>\n<p><span>While supplies last and will be updated weekly.\u00a0 Sometime we have soaps that are just a bit underweight to be sold with our regular soaps (4.5 - 5.5 oz).\u00a0 Still great soap, and a heck of a deal!\u00a0\u00a0</span></p>\n<p><span>\u00a0If cart does not allow you to add more, it means we've sold out.</span></p>\n<p>3.5\u00a0- 4.5 oz.<br></p>\n<div class=\"ProductDescriptionContainer\">\n<p><strong><span>Amazing Ingredients!</span></strong></p>\n<p>Saponified Oils of Palm, Coconut &amp; Olive Oil. Essential &amp;/or Fragrance Oils, may contain herbs, jojoba beads, oats.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
