    "https://3e37aa.myshopify.com": {
      "product": {
        "id": 10337294090515,
        "title": "BLEMISHED NO-FOAM Rawhide Durra-Bull Premium Leatherette\u00ae Sheets (12x24)",
        "handle": "blemished-no-foam-rawhide-durra-bull-premium-leatherette\u00ae-sheets-12x24",
        "body_html": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 42, 0);\"><strong>All sales final and not discount eligible. At least 90% or more of the sheet is useable. May include blemishes such as scratches, wrinkles, or were the end of the roll during production and have an unsealed side (can very easily add adhesive and press to mitigate the issue). They're sold WITH adhesive only.</strong></span></p>\n<p><strong>(These sheets come without the foam backing so they are thinner and more suited for beanies and clothing.)\u00a0</strong></p>\n<p>These faux leather panels come in\u00a0an array of colors to match any request your customer throws at you. Shipped ready to use these panels are backed by the industry leading thermal activated adhesive Durra-Bull.<br></p>\n<p>Panel dimensions are 12in x 24in\u00a0</p>\n<p>For best results engrave with little to no air and clean remaining char with LA Awesome(or something similar) and a brush.\u00a0</p>\n<p><strong>Note:\u00a0</strong><em>The Foam and NO-FOAM option relates to the backing material which is sandwiched\u00a0between the engraving surface and the back surface of the leatherette.\u00a0</em></p>\n<p><em>Through thorough testing we have found that the NO-FOAM version of the leatherette is the best option for adhering to beanies and other articles of clothing which may require occasional machine washing.\u00a0 The leatherette with foam backing is best for use on items which will be hand-washed only.Full\u00a0</em></p>\n<p>For best results, engrave with as little air as possible, while turning it back on for the cutting phase. Clean remaining char with LA Awesome (or something similar - many use a degreaser from Harbor Freight) and an old toothbrush.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>A spreadsheet of suggested settings is available\u00a0<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/19RsZNkWHiuVC7U0SFDEVjQTbd5JJCixb0g8VL_tkdeY/edit?fbclid=IwY2xjawFFUgNleHRuA2FlbQIxMAABHezrserh1WIYWq-B6rU-rhAA4iODNYS2_FJ_qWn93XH8yu68rkkd8nlVeA_aem_-pwOmf43r9fQ2HH2NqsV6A&amp;gid=84907358#gid=84907358\" title=\"Laser Settings Spreadsheet\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">HERE</a>, which is populated by customers in our active Facebook group linked below. Don't see what you need? Join &amp; ask or use the search function - we have an incredibly helpful community.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Note:<span>\u00a0</span></strong><em>LoneStar Adhesive has made every attempt to ensure that photos of our materials accurately reflect the color you will see in person. However, there are natural variances between all digital screens and what our human eyes perceive. If you need an exact color match, please consider first reviewing the additional product photos (when available), purchasing a\u00a0<a href=\"https://lonestaradhesive.com/products/sample-set-of-durra-bull-premium-leatherette%E2%84%A2-sheets-2x4\" title=\"Sample Set\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">sample set</a>, or joining our<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/lonestaradhesiveofficial\" title=\"LoneStar Adhesive Facebook Group\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><span>\u00a0</span>Facebook group</a><span>\u00a0</span>to see a multitude of examples that others have posted. We look forward to seeing what you create!</em></p>",
        "published_at": "2026-03-28T22:11:49-05:00",
        "created_at": "2026-03-10T14:24:19-05:00",
        "updated_at": "2026-04-02T12:59:46-05:00",
