    "https://kitchenkapers.myshopify.com": {
      "product": {
        "id": 8507546435780,
        "title": "Now Designs Love Is Love Mug",
        "handle": "now-designs-love-is-love-mug",
        "body_html": "<p>A rainbow arcs across the sky in a parade of color on the Now Designs Love Is Love Mug. Complimenting pops of color are glazed onto the handle and rim. The 20 oz capacity and durable stoneware construction will keep your beverage warm as long the conversations last.\u00a0 This fully glazed stoneware mug is dishwasher and microwave safe. Measures 3.75\" dia. x 3.75\" h.</p>\n<p><strong>Features of the Now Designs Love Is Love Mug \u00a0include:</strong></p>\n<ul></ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Durable glazed stoneware</li>\n<li>Beautiful rainbow design</li>\n<li>20 oz capacity</li>\n<li>Ideal for any hot beverage</li>\n<li>Dishwasher and microwave safe</li>\n<li>3.75\" dia x 3.75\" h</li>\n</ul>",
        "published_at": "2026-02-22T15:02:34-05:00",
