        "handle": "nirvana-really-easy-guitar-01422006",
        "body_html": "<p><span>Unleash your inner grunge with\u00a0</span><i>Nirvana \u2013 Really Easy Guitar</i><span>! This new addition to Hal Leonard's Really Easy Guitar series features 14 iconic songs with simple chords, lyrics, and basic tab \u2013 perfect for beginners. With easy-to-follow charts, you'll be playing your favorite Nirvana hits in no time!</span><br><br><span>Songs include: About a Girl \u2022 Come as You Are \u2022 Heart Shaped Box \u2022 Lithium \u2022 Smells Like Teen Spirit \u2022 and more.</span></p>",
