    "https://valuepetsupplies-com.myshopify.com": {
      "product": {
        "id": 14995157057902,
        "title": "ValueBull USA Pork Hide Retriever Rolls for Dogs, 4 Inch Pig Skin Chews, 50 Count",
        "handle": "valuebull-usa-pork-hide-retriever-rolls-for-dogs-4-inch-pig-skin-chews-50-count",
        "body_html": "<p data-start=\"25\" data-end=\"315\">Give your dog a chew they\u2019ll truly love with <strong data-start=\"70\" data-end=\"120\">ValueBull USA Pig Skin Retriever Rolls, 4 Inch</strong>\u2014a natural, satisfying chew made from <strong data-start=\"158\" data-end=\"180\">100% USA pork hide</strong>. These compact retriever rolls deliver a flavorful chewing experience that keeps dogs engaged while supporting healthy chewing habits.</p><p data-start=\"317\" data-end=\"645\">Crafted from high-quality <strong data-start=\"343\" data-end=\"372\">American-sourced pig skin</strong>, these natural dog chews offer a dense texture that encourages longer chew sessions compared to traditional rawhide. The rich, naturally savory aroma (the kind dogs go crazy for) makes these rolls irresistible while providing a productive outlet for dogs who love to chew.</p><p data-start=\"647\" data-end=\"954\">Each <strong data-start=\"652\" data-end=\"677\">4-inch retriever roll</strong> is sized perfectly for small to medium dogs or as a quick reward for larger breeds. Because these treats are made from <strong data-start=\"797\" data-end=\"818\">natural pork hide</strong>, variations in color, shape, and smell are completely normal\u2014and proof you\u2019re giving your dog a minimally processed, protein-rich chew.</p><p>\n\n\n</p><p data-start=\"956\" data-end=\"1164\">Whether used as a reward, boredom buster, or everyday chew, <strong data-start=\"1016\" data-end=\"1058\">ValueBull USA Pig Skin Retriever Rolls</strong> deliver a simple ingredient chew dogs crave while helping redirect chewing away from furniture and shoes.</p><p><br><i>Supervision is recommended when giving your dog any treat. Introduce new protein-rich natural treats (a treat your pet has never eaten before) on a gradual basis (one every three days). We recommend no more than one pig skin roll per day until your pet has been acclimated to them. Always provide plenty of fresh water. Wash your hands after handling any chew or treat. Store in a dry place at room temperature.</i></p>",
        "published_at": "2026-03-18T12:43:42-05:00",
        "created_at": "2026-03-18T11:02:35-05:00",
        "updated_at": "2026-04-02T12:59:47-05:00",
