ms of these products.</span></span></span><u><span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:'Segoe UI'\"><span style=\"color:#212b36\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><span style=\"text-underline:single\"></span></span></span></span></span></u></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:12.0000pt; text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:'Segoe UI'\"><span style=\"color:#212b36\">We hope you feel comfortable and confident when shopping at </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\u5b8b\u4f53\"><span style=\"color:#212b36\"><font face=\"Segoe UI\">OlyVogue</font></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:'Segoe UI'\"><span style=\"color:#212b36\">, that\u2019s why we offer an easy 18-day return &amp; exchange policy.</span></span></span> <a href=\"http://olyvogue.com/pages/easy-return\"><u><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:'Segoe UI'\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><span style=\"text-underline:single\">Learn more</span></span></span></span></span></u></a><u><span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\u5b8b\u4f53\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><span style=\"text-underline:single\"></span></span></span></span></span></u></p>\n\n<p><b><span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:'Segoe UI'\"><span style=\"color:#212b36\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold\">Any concern, please Contact Customer Service team online or by email.</span></span></span></span></b></p>\n",
