        "body_html": "<p><meta charset=\"utf-8\">This <strong data-end=\"3403\" data-start=\"3366\">14mm gold plated spiral coin bead</strong> features a radiant finish and a symbolic spiral motif, with a <strong data-end=\"3478\" data-start=\"3466\">1mm hole</strong> for easy stringing. The spiral represents growth, transformation, and the unfolding journey of life.</p>\n<p>In <strong>a Blessingway</strong> necklace, it serves as a powerful symbol of motherhood and the evolving path of both mother and child. The gold tone adds warmth, light, and a sense of celebration to the design.\u00a0 Sold individually.</p>",
        "published_at": "2026-03-16T20:59:58-04:00",
        "created_at": "2026-03-16T20:57:05-04:00",
        "updated_at": "2026-04-02T13:59:47-04:00",
