    "https://fishandsave.myshopify.com": {
      "product": {
        "id": 10406409044149,
        "title": "FAS Newbility High Quality Plastic Fishing Bell Alarm 4.5cm 8g Qty 1",
        "handle": "newbility-high-quality-plastic-rod-sea-fishing-bell-alarm-4-5cm-8g",
        "body_html": "<p>FAS<span> </span>Newbility High Quality Plastic Rod Sea Fishing Bell Alarm<span aria-label=\"Go to product viewer dialog for this item.\"></span><span>\u00a0is a clip-on bite indicator designed specifically for sea and night fishing. These alarms feature a dual-bell system that provides a loud audible alert when a fish strikes, allowing you to manage multiple rods without needing to watch them constantly.</span></p>\n<ul data-processed=\"true\" data-complete=\"true\" data-sfc-cb=\"\" data-sfc-root=\"c\" class=\"KsbFXc U6u95\">\n<li data-sae=\"\" data-complete=\"true\" data-hveid=\"CAQQAA\" data-sfc-cb=\"\" data-sfc-root=\"c\" class=\"dF3vjf\"><span data-complete=\"true\" data-sfc-cb=\"\" data-sfc-root=\"c\" data-sfc-cp=\"\" class=\"T286Pc\"><strong data-complete=\"true\" data-sfc-cb=\"\" data-sfc-root=\"c\" class=\"Yjhzub\">Design &amp; Material</strong>: Constructed from durable ABS plastic clips and metal alloy bells, designed to resist corrosion from saltwater and exposure to the elements.</span></li>\n<li data-sae=\"\" data-complete=\"true\" data-hveid=\"CAQQAQ\" data-sfc-cb=\"\" data-sfc-root=\"c\" class=\"dF3vjf\"><span data-complete=\"true\" data-sfc-cb=\"\" data-sfc-root=\"c\" data-sfc-cp=\"\" class=\"T286Pc\"><strong data-complete=\"true\" data-sfc-cb=\"\" data-sfc-root=\"c\" class=\"Yjhzub\">Dimensions &amp; Weight</strong>: Each unit typically measures approximately<span>\u00a0</span><strong data-complete=\"true\" data-sfc-cb=\"\" data-sfc-root=\"c\" class=\"Yjhzub\">4.5cm to 4.6cm</strong><span>\u00a0</span>in length and weighs about<span>\u00a0</span><strong data-complete=\"true\" data-sfc-cb=\"\" data-sfc-root=\"c\" class=\"Yjhzub\">8g</strong>, making them lightweight enough to not interfere with the rod's balance.</span></li>\n<li data-sae=\"\" data-complete=\"true\" data-hveid=\"CAQQAg\" data-sfc-cb=\"\" data-sfc-root=\"c\" class=\"dF3vjf\"><span data-complete=\"true\" data-sfc-cb=\"\" data-sfc-root=\"c\" data-sfc-cp=\"\" class=\"T286Pc\"><strong data-complete=\"true\" data-sfc-cb=\"\" data-sfc-root=\"c\" class=\"Yjhzub\">Dual Alert System</strong>: Features two bells per clip to produce a louder, clearer sound that can be heard even in windy or noisy coastal conditions.</span></li>\n<li data-sae=\"\" data-complete=\"true\" data-hveid=\"CAQQAw\" data-sfc-cb=\"\" data-sfc-root=\"c\" class=\"dF3vjf\"><span aria-owns=\"action-menu-parent-container\" data-complete=\"true\" data-sfc-cb=\"\" data-sfc-root=\"c\" data-sfc-cp=\"\" class=\"T286Pc\"><strong data-complete=\"true\" data-sfc-cb=\"\" data-sfc-root=\"c\" class=\"Yjhzub\">Secure Attachment</strong>: Equipped with high-tension plastic clamps that provide a strong grip on the rod tip to prevent the alarm from falling off during a strike</span></li>\n</ul>",
        "published_at": "2026-04-02T07:27:52-07:00",
        "created_at": "2026-04-02T07:23:19-07:00",
        "updated_at": "2026-04-02T10:59:47-07:00",
