        "id": 1809223745570,
        "title": "Jellycat Bashful Grey Bunny, Medium",
        "handle": "jellycat-bashful-grey-bunny-medium",
        "body_html": "<h2>The fair price of our product will suit you!</h2>\n<p>Nowadays toy industry is a very progressive and high-tech sphere and our store is offering you only the best products. Of course you remember your toys because they\u2019re unforgettable. Our manufacturers and vendors guarantee the premium quality of our toys.\u00a0This is a very important aspect because nowadays we have a great number of fakes. You must be aware because fakes are very dangerous for your kids. You can address our online support system if you want to know more. All toys are well-designed and we are sure that your kids will like it.\u00a0Moreover - you can save some money.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Age Range\u00a0</li>\n<li>Dolls and soft toys</li>\n<li>Playsets</li>\n<li>Collectibles</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Because we often provide different promos and you can get some benefits. Our products are well-designed and they are totally safe for your child\u2019s health. We\u2019ve created our small world. This is a very important aspect because nowadays we have a great number of fakes. You must be aware because fakes are very dangerous for your kids.You can address our online support system if you want to know more.</p>\n<h2>We can satisfy any whim of our little clients</h2>\n<p>Because we often provide different promos and you can get some benefits. Our products are well-designed and they are totally safe for your child\u2019s health. We\u2019ve created our small world. This is a very important aspect because nowadays we have a great number of fakes. You must be aware because fakes are very dangerous for your kids.</p>\n<p>Children explore outer world with the help of simple senses \u2013 sense of smell, touch, sight and others. This is a very important aspect because nowadays we have a great number of fakes. \u00a0You can address our online support system if you want to know more. Kids are the best explorers in the world. Our products are well-designed and they are totally safe for your child\u2019s health.\u00a0</p>\n<p><strong>You can address our online support system if you want to know more.</strong></p>",
        "published_at": "2019-04-03T06:06:01-04:00",
        "created_at": "2019-04-03T06:06:16-04:00",
        "updated_at": "2026-04-02T13:43:41-04:00",
