        "id": 7828964311101,
        "title": "Empaca Tank - Women's",
        "handle": "empaca-tank-womens-1",
        "body_html": "<p>Whether you\u2019re pedaling around town, jogging through the woods, or perusing farmer\u2019s market stalls, the Empaca Tank is a summer staple. The blend of recycled polyester, TENCEL\u2122, and spandex is stretchy and breathable, ideal for bite-sized adventures and bucket list trips alike.</p>",
