        "title": "SKIMS STRETCH MENS KNIT BOXER | OBSIDIAN",
        "handle": "skims-stretch-mens-knit-boxer-obsidian",
        "body_html": "<p><meta charset=\"utf-8\">No other knit boxer compares. Our four-way stretch fabric that never loses shape, now in a knit boxer. Designed with a looser waistband for maximum comfort and a slimmer leg opening for the perfect fit under pants. Includes a jacquard SKIMS logo on the waist and functional fly opening. Inseam measures 5\u201d.</p>",
