        "body_html": "<p> Let your inner compass lead. The Soul Guide Spirit Crop Tank is a soft reminder to trust the path, worn on the mat, in the meditation corner, and every moment you show up for yourself. </p>\n<ul>\n<li> Worn-in feel without the wear </li>\n<li> Soul Guide graphic illuminates your path forward </li>\n<li>  Crew neck, relaxed fit </li>\n<li> Cropped length, dropped armhole </li>\n<li> Thoughtfully made in LA </li>\n</ul>",
