        "handle": "apres-short-in-heather-oat-crepe-2603",
        "body_html": "<p>The Apres Short in Heather Oat Crepe from Taylor Stitch</p><ul>\n<li>9.5-oz. 55% linen, 45% organic cotton crepe.\n</li>\n<li>6-oz. 100% organic cotton SF map pocketing.\n</li>\n<li>Washed for a soft, lived in feel.\n</li>\n<li>Elastic waistband with drawcord.\n</li>\n<li>Button fly.\n</li>\n<li>Two front slash front pockets.\n</li>\n<li>Two back patch button-through pockets.\n</li>\n<li>Wash cold and tumble dry low.\n</li>\n<li>Made in China.</li>\n</ul>\n",
