    "https://www.fillupbuttercup.com": {
      "product": {
        "id": 9323978916148,
        "title": "LAUNDRY DETERGENT LIQUID BY THE CLEANER SOUL",
        "handle": "laundry-detergent-liquid-by-the-cleaner-soul",
        "body_html": "<p><span>\u273d</span><span> Available at our <a title=\"How our fill up bar works.\" href=\"https://www.fillupbuttercup.com/pages/how-it-works\">fill up bar</a> for .50 an ounce</span>\u00a0<span>\u273d</span></p>\n<p><span>Keep your clothes fresh and clean with ease. Just 2\u20133 tablespoons of our gentle laundry detergent is all you need per load. Available in breathe <strong data-start=\"274\" data-end=\"288\">Eucalyptus</strong> or\u00a0<strong data-start=\"300\" data-end=\"312\">Lavender </strong>love, The Cleaner Soul's formula uses <strong data-start=\"331\" data-end=\"360\" data-is-only-node=\"\">simple, clean ingredients</strong> you can feel good about. Perfect for those who want effective cleaning without unnecessary chemicals.</span></p>",
        "published_at": "2026-03-29T19:18:25-07:00",
