        "title": "Sampler Surprise",
        "handle": "stocking-stuffer-tester",
        "body_html": "<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<p>Searching for the perfect small gift or ultimate crowd-pleaser for your next party? Look no further!</p>\n<p>Each present pouch features 2 Coffee Dust flavors, and the excitement lies in the element of surprise. After receiving your gift, elevate the enjoyment by trading flavors with your friends, family, or colleagues.</p>\n<p>Every tin contains\u00a012 servings of delightful flavors to enhance your coffee experience. Gift a fresh twist to your everyone\u2019s morning routines!</p>",
