    "https://www.malie.com": {
      "product": {
        "id": 7969106100339,
        "title": "Mango Nectar Island Ambiance Mist Mini",
        "handle": "mango-nectar-island-ambiance-mist-mini",
        "body_html": "<p><span color=\"#930156\" style=\"color: #930156;\"><strong>Introducing a new 5ml mini size, perfect for travel or a little moment of aloha on the go!\u00a0</strong></span></p>\n<p>Create an uplifting, tropical atmosphere with this portable Island Ambiance Mist.</p>\n<p>Simply spray to scent any space, refresh fabrics, or enjoy as a light perfume.\u00a0Perfect for linens, luggage and personal use, it brings a touch of paradise wherever you go.</p>\n<p>Made with aloha using wild-crafted Hawaiian Hydrosols. Spray liberally.</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #930156;\"><strong>70% Organic Ingredients:\u00a0</strong></span>Natural Grain Alcohol (denat), Water, Fragrance, Hawaiian Hydrosols.</p>\n<p><em>Cruelty-free and vegan. Free from parabens, silicone, sulfates, mineral oil, phthalates, petrochemicals, talc and gluten.</em></p>\n<p>5 ml</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #930156;\"><strong>mango nectar<br></strong></span><meta charset=\"utf-8\">A sweet and sassy cocktail of mouthwatering tropical fruits. This aroma is an energizing blend of ripe mango, juicy apricot and succulent papaya accompanied by pulpy oranges touched by island sunshine.\u00a0<br><span>\u2022 Top: Mango, Orange</span><br><span>\u2022 Mid: Papaya, Melon, Apricot</span><br><span>\u2022 Base: Musk</span><br></p>",
        "published_at": "2025-04-25T11:44:15-10:00",
        "created_at": "2025-04-24T11:56:07-10:00",
        "updated_at": "2026-04-02T08:53:00-10:00",
