        "title": "Diablo Rojo Medium",
        "handle": "diablo-rojo-medium-1",
        "body_html": "<div class=\"relative basis-auto flex-col -mb-(--composer-overlap-px) [--composer-overlap-px:28px] grow flex overflow-hidden\">\n<div class=\"relative h-full\">\n<div class=\"flex h-full flex-col overflow-y-auto thread-xl:pt-(--header-height) [scrollbar-gutter:stable_both-edges]\">\n<div class=\"flex flex-col text-sm thread-xl:pt-header-height pb-25\">\n<article class=\"text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none [--shadow-height:45px] has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) has-data-writing-block:pt-(--shadow-height) [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto [content-visibility:auto] supports-[content-visibility:auto]:[contain-intrinsic-size:auto_100lvh] scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]\" dir=\"auto\" data-turn-id=\"04cebdb0-d9ff-47d3-893f-b941d2fa7f1b\" data-testid=\"conversation-turn-22\" data-scroll-anchor=\"true\" data-turn=\"assistant\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"text-base my-auto mx-auto pb-10 [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] thread-sm:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] thread-lg:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(16)] px-(--thread-content-margin)\">\n<div class=\"[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] thread-lg:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"flex max-w-full flex-col grow\">\n<div data-message-author-role=\"assistant\" data-message-id=\"7c0c5a76-a888-4ec9-8e3c-a25862ca5b84\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1\" data-message-model-slug=\"gpt-5-1-thinking\">\n<div class=\"flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]\">\n<div class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words light markdown-new-styling\">\n<blockquote data-start=\"77\" data-end=\"1452\">\n<p data-start=\"79\" data-end=\"366\"><strong>Diablo Rojo</strong> is an addictive, restaurant-style, smoky, chunky chipotle salsa like no other. Each small batch is made by hand with locally sourced, premium ingredients\u2014ripe tomatoes, garlic, smoky chipotle peppers, a bit of heat from jalape\u00f1os, and bright, fresh-squeezed lime juice.</p>\n<p data-start=\"373\" data-end=\"777\">With every bite, your mouth experiences layers of flavor: first the natural sweetness of the tomatoes, then the tang of fresh lime, followed by a deep, smoky undertone\u2014and finally, a warm jalape\u00f1o spice that lingers just long enough to make you crave another chip to dip. It\u2019s chunky, never thin, with a medium spice level that brings a warm, smoky kick\u2014exciting and bold without overpowering the dish.</p>\n<p data-start=\"784\" data-end=\"1165\"><strong data-start=\"784\" data-end=\"832\">From Dip to Dish \u2013 instantly upgrade dinner.</strong> Scoop it with chips or use it as a ready-to-go cooking sauce for tacos, enchiladas, fajitas, eggs, burgers, bowls, grilled shrimp, and roasted veggies. Pour it over chicken, simmer it with shrimp, stir it into roasted veggies, or bake it over enchiladas for a fast, flavor-packed meal without a long ingredient list or extra prep.</p>\n<p data-start=\"1172\" data-end=\"1452\"><strong data-start=\"1172\" data-end=\"1206\">Family-Owned &amp; Purpose-Driven:</strong> Created by a mom and her three sons, every jar of Diablo Rojo is part of their mission-driven Diablo line that supports wildlife and conservation. A portion of the proceeds is donated to help clean up our beautiful oceans and save marine life.</p>\n<p data-start=\"1172\" data-end=\"1452\">NOTE - PLEASE EXCUSE the lack of proper product shots, they are on their way.\u00a0 Do not stress, your salsa will come labeled, we are just working on proper product shots.\u00a0 Thank you for your understanding!\u00a0\u00a0</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p data-start=\"1454\" data-end=\"1590\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\"><br></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mt-3 w-full empty:hidden\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
