        "id": 7744331251830,
        "title": "Minicake/Shorty Patch Cable 6 Inch",
        "handle": "minicake-shorty-patch-cable-6-inch",
        "body_html": "<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>These Patch Cables are made with our ultra small Minicake right angle connectors on one end and our Short straight barreled \"Shorty\" connectors on the other. The cable is our flexible extra low capacitance 5mm CMC-05 Instrument Cable.\u00a0</p>\n<p>Features:<br></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Soldered by humans</li>\n<li>6 inches Plug to Plug</li>\n<li>Minicake Right Angle and Shorty Plugs</li>\n<li>Ultra flexible CMC-05 Instrument Cable</li>\n<li>Spiral Shield</li>\n<li>Heat Shrink for strain relief</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\u00a0</p>",
