    "https://dingall.com": {
      "product": {
        "id": 6706777161894,
        "title": "Ding All Multi-purpose Wax comb and Fin Key",
        "handle": "ding-all-multi-purpose-wax-comb-and-fin-key",
        "body_html": "<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p data-mce-fragment=\"1\">A wax comb is a tool used in the maintenance and removal of surfboard wax on a surfboard. It is important for wax combs to come equipped with features such a jagged or toothed edge and a straight, relatively sharp edge.</p>\n<p data-mce-fragment=\"1\">The Ding All Multi Wax Comb is a necessary tool to have on-hand to remove wax, create friction when needed. Now equipped with a bonus fin key!!</p>\n<p data-mce-fragment=\"1\"><strong>Details:\u00a0</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<strong>Colors:</strong> Clear\u00a0</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Features:\u00a0</strong>Scrapes Flat, and Rails, Deep teeth for Combing, and a bonus Fin Key.</li>\n</ul>",
