        "handle": "39966-car-vehicle-puffy-sticker-12",
        "body_html": "<p>39966 Car &amp; Vehicle Puffy Sticker-12</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"2\" face=\"Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\" size=\"3\"><span color=\"#000000\" face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"3\">$1.20 each sheet x 12 sheets each pack </span></span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"2\" face=\"Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\" size=\"3\"><span color=\"#000000\" face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"3\">$14.40 for 12 sheets of same design.</span></span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"2\" face=\"Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\" size=\"3\"><span color=\"#000000\" face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"3\">These amazing stickers can add personality to any notes, letter, planner, and more! Get creative and mix and match multiple stickers to create unique new stories. Perfect for all ages especially\u00a0for high school and college!\u00a0</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 1.4em;\">\u00a0</span><br></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"2\" face=\"Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\" size=\"3\"><span><br></span></span></span></p>",
