    "https://www.sixthandzero.com": {
      "product": {
        "id": 7913180332115,
        "title": "Upcycled Hacky Sack / Footbag",
        "handle": "upcycled-hacky-sack-footbag",
        "body_html": "<p><span>The Footbag is a versatile game, gender-neutral and multi-generational. It can be as simple or as complicated as you make it! Made from upcycled sari fabrics. The work specifically supports women artisan makers, who take discarded traditional dress fabric and repurpose it into functional and fun products.</span></p>\n<p><span>Each item is unique, you cannot choose.</span></p>\n<div class=\"mb-2\">\n<p class=\"f_t_base f_t_color f_t_paragraphSansRegular\">Made in India</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mb-2\">\n<p class=\"f_t_base f_t_color f_t_paragraphSansRegular\">Product Language: English</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mb-2\">\n<p class=\"f_t_base f_t_color f_t_paragraphSansRegular\">Weight: 1.2 oz (34.02 g)</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mb-2\">\n<p class=\"f_t_base f_t_color f_t_paragraphSansRegular\">Dimensions: 0 x 2 x 0 in (0 x 5.1 x 0 cm)</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mb-2\">\n<p class=\"f_t_base f_t_color f_t_paragraphSansRegular\">UPC: 780729495096</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mt-2 mb-2\">\n<p class=\"f_t_base f_t_color f_t_paragraphSansMedium\">Eco-friendly information</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mb-2\">\n<p class=\"f_t_base f_t_color f_t_paragraphSansRegular\">Product Materials: Plastic-free and Recycled</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mb-2\">\n<p class=\"f_t_base f_t_color f_t_paragraphSansRegular\">Packaging: Recyclable</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mb-2\">\n<p class=\"f_t_base f_t_color f_t_paragraphSansRegular\">Production: Ethically sourced and Fair trade</p>\n</div>\n<p>\u00a0</p>",
