        "id": 7582405361814,
        "title": "Custom Dual Colored Small Flat Arrowhead Tags",
        "handle": "custom-dual-colored-small-flat-arrowhead-tags",
        "body_html": "<p>Small in size. Big in capability. This <strong data-start=\"2302\" data-end=\"2343\">Custom Engraved Small All-Weather Tag</strong> brings rugged reliability to <strong data-start=\"2373\" data-end=\"2426\">inventory systems, cages, gates, posts, and tools</strong>.<br data-start=\"2427\" data-end=\"2430\"></p>\n<p>Your custom engraving stays readable through the toughest conditions\u2014designed for operations that need precise, compact labeling.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Perfect for small assets or tight spaces</li>\n<li>Custom engraving ensures lasting identification</li>\n<li>Used in agriculture, facilities, and scientific research</li>\n</ul>",
