    "https://thefloramodiste.com": {
      "product": {
        "id": 4564448411699,
        "title": "Face Mask",
        "handle": "face-mask",
        "body_html": "<p>Every single one of our handmade face masks is cut and sewn by yours truly.</p>\n<p><strong>Here's what goes into our masks:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<strong>TWO layers of woven fabric.</strong>\u00a0All of our fabrics are\u00a0woven (not knit)\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.nbcnews.com/health/health-news/making-your-own-face-mask-some-fabrics-work-better-others-n1175966?cid=sm_npd_nn_fb_ma&amp;fbclid=IwAR3uMluYWbQlC7bD0CUnjaTOuMutr8ux1TmbUUg1FUYOBNy2NIYkqOauIKw\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Why we use woven fabrics for our face masks\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">which are more likely to block viral particles.</a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Fabric ties that tie around the head, not the ear.</strong> Masks that tie behind the head contour more to your face than elastic bands that just fit behind the ear. Elastic also wears out--Our fabric ties do not and will work for years to come.</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Pleated design allows for faces of all sizes.</strong> If you have a smaller face, don't let the pleats out as much. If you need the full width of the mask (as most people will) you can let out the entire mask.</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Reversible mask options!</strong> All of our masks are sewn with two different layers of fabric so that you can mix and match your masks.</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Machine washable.</strong> All of our masks are machine washable--Washing your masks is highly recommended after use, to help keep yourself healthy.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>PLEASE NOTE:</strong> Our masks do not have an opening for a filter.</p>\n<p>You can also sew your own DIY face mask! <a href=\"https://www.thefloramodiste.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/How-To-Make-A-Face-Mask-Opt-In.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"DIY sewing tutorial: How to make a face mask\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Download the free PDF tutorial here.</a></p>\n<p><b><u>FACE MASK MEASUREMENTS</u></b></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Laying flat with the pleats closed: 7.25\" wide x 3.5\" tall</li>\n<li>Wearing the mask, fully extended: 7.25\" wide x 6.5\" tall</li>\n<li>Mask ties: 17\" long</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Due to the custom nature of face masks, all sales are final.</p>",
