    "https://utmprinting.com": {
      "product": {
        "id": 10318725349650,
        "title": "Cute Easter Bunny, Funny 6 7 Meme DTF Transfer, Funny Bunny Easter Shirt Design",
        "handle": "cute-easter-bunny-funny-6-7-meme-dtf-transfer-funny-bunny-easter-shirt-design",
        "body_html": "<h1 class=\"text-14 min-[575px]:text-24 mb-4 font-bold\">Cute Easter Bunny, Funny 6 7 Meme DTF Transfer, Funny Bunny Easter Shirt Design</h1>\n<h2><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 42, 0);\"><strong>DTF TRANSFER FILM ONLY!</strong></span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 42, 0);\">The size information provided (e.g., Adult XS (10\"x14.5\") represents the maximum dimensions of the design. The first value is the <strong>width</strong>, and the second value is the <strong>height</strong>.<strong>(W\" x H\")</strong> Depending on the design's proportions, either the <strong>width </strong>or <strong>height </strong>will be set to the maximum value mentioned, ensuring the design maintains its original aspect ratio.\"</span></p>\n<div class=\"image-with-text__text rte body\">\n<p><strong>HIGHLIGHTS:</strong></p>\n<p><span>- ANYTIME PEEL DTF FILM (Hot/Cold Peel)</span><br><span>- Vibrant And Solid Colors!</span><br><span>- High quality transfer films. Easy Peel and Ultra Stretchy!</span><br><span>- Can be pressed on Any kind and color of FABRICS, LEATHER, PATCHES!</span><br><span>- Ultra Durable! 100+ Washes!</span><br><span>- Soft to Touch!</span><br><span>- 100% Satisfaction Guaranteed!</span><br><span>- No Minimums or Setup Fee!</span><br><span>- Fast Turnaround ( 99.99% of orders ship in</span><strong><span>\u00a0</span>SAME DAY!</strong><span>)</span><br><span>- Can be pressed onto a variety of fabrics (T-shirts, sweatshirts, hoodies, polo shirts, dress shirts, hats, bags and more)</span></p>\n</div>\n<p><span><strong>HOW TO ORDER ?</strong></span></p>\n<p>1- Order the number of DTF transfer films by sizes.</p>\n<p>2- We print your DTF transfer films and ship them to you as soon as possible.</p>\n<p><span><strong>HOW TO APPLY ANYTIME PEEL FILM ?</strong></span></p>\n<p><span>1. \u00a0 \u00a0Set heat press temperature and timer. (See details below)<br>2. \u00a0 \u00a0Set pressure to medium (60LB of pressure)<br>3. \u00a0 \u00a0Place your garment onto the heat press.<br>4. \u00a0 \u00a0Place your DTF film onto desired place on your garment. (If you want to protect the film and garment from overheating, you can place Teflon or parchment paper over the film.)<br>5. \u00a0 \u00a0Press it 3-5 sec.<br>6. \u00a0 You can carefully peel the film immediately after pressing (maximum 5 seconds)\u00a0<strong>OR\u00a0</strong>after it has cooled completely.<br>7. \u00a0 \u00a0Post-press for an additional 3-5 seconds to remove any additional adhesive and to make the print last longer.</span></p>\n<p><span><strong>TEMPERATURE</strong><br>COTTON: 325F<br>POLYESTERS: 275F<br>TRI BLENDS: 275F<br>50/50 BLENDS: 300F</span></p>\n<p><span><strong>GARMENT TYPES</strong><br>DTF works with almost all fabrics and garment types. Cottons, Combined-Cottons, Tri-Blends, 50/50 Blends, Polyesters, Blended Fabrics, Leather, Vinyl, Denim, Canvas and more\u2026</span></p>",
        "published_at": "2026-03-06T14:42:36-08:00",
        "created_at": "2026-03-06T14:42:36-08:00",
