        "body_html": "<p>These beautiful non-religious commitment cards have the following text on them:</p>\n<p><em>\u201cFrom this day forward, regardless of my past mistakes, I promise to respect myself and others, pursue a life of purity, and save the gift of my sexuality for marriage.\u201d</em></p>\n<p>To purchase these commitment cards in bulk,\u00a0<a href=\"https://shop.chastity.com/products/commitment-card-non-religious-pack-of-20?utm_source=copyToPasteBoard&amp;utm_medium=product-links&amp;utm_content=web\">click here.</a>\u00a0To purchase the faith-based version of this commitment card, <a href=\"https://chastity-project.myshopify.com/products/commitment-card\">click here.</a></p>\n<!---->",
