        "id": 4248679415882,
        "title": "Vanilla Bean Lip Balm",
        "handle": "vanilla-bean-lip-balm",
        "body_html": "<p style=\"background-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; color: #3b3b3b; font-family: &amp;quot; lato&amp;quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 18.34px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The most luscious vanilla-scented lip balm you will ever have the pleasure of applying to your lips. It will help to hydrate, moisturize, and give the slightest glisten to your smile.</span></p>\n<p style=\"background-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; color: #3b3b3b; font-family: &amp;quot; lato&amp;quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 18.34px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><meta charset=\"utf-8\"> <span><strong>Ingredients:</strong> Castor Oil, Palm Kernel Oil, Beeswax, Sunflower Oil, Jojoba Oil, Vitamin E, Stevia, and Flavor Oil.\u00a0</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"background-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; color: #3b3b3b; font-family: &amp;quot; lato&amp;quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 18.34px 0px;\">\u00a0<a href=\"https://livingthegoodlifenaturally.com/policies/refund-policy\" title=\"Refund Policy\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Shipping &amp; Refund Policies\u00a0</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"background-color: 