        "body_html": "<p><span>These are</span><span> sold as pictured. The color of the metal &amp; findings cannot be changed, however if you would like to swap the earring findings for lever backs, wire hoops or clip ons, please add this listing to your cart before purchase :\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.peripheral.us/products/lever-back-clip-on-substitutes\">LEVER BACKS / CLIP ONS</a></span></p>\n<p><span>Please see the FAQ page of my website before purchase to understand my shop policies, or if you have any questions at all about ordering/receiving my products.</span></p>\n<p>metal color: silver<br>weight: 3 grams</p>",
