    "https://www.swiitcreations.com": {
      "product": {
        "id": 7915192254547,
        "title": "Oh For F\u2019s Sake Floral UV DTF Cup Decal | UV1993",
        "handle": "oh-for-fs-sake-floral-uv-dtf-cup-decal-uv-1993-427513760",
        "body_html": "<p>This UV DTF cup decal features a colorful floral wreath with a cheeky quote for a bold design that mixes sweet flowers with sarcastic attitude. It is a fun choice for drinkware, gifts, and anyone who loves playful statement art with a bright retro inspired look.</p><br><p>Upgrade your tumbler with a durable UV DTF wrap designed for smooth, professional results \u2728 Each transfer is printed for strong adhesion, crisp detail, and long-lasting color on hard surfaces like glass, acrylic, and metal \ud83e\udd64</p><br><p>Available Sizes:\u2028</p><p>\u2705 16oz Libbey Glass / 40oz Tumblers</p><p>\u2028\u2705 12oz Stainless Steel / 15oz Ceramic Coffee Mugs</p><br><p>Why You\u2019ll Love It:</p><p>Easy Application:\u00a0No heat press required. Just peel, place, and press.</p><p>Built to Last:\u00a0Fully\u00a0waterproof\u00a0and\u00a0scratch-resistant\u00a0for everyday durability. \ud83d\udca7</p><br><p>Care Instructions:\u00a0</p><p>To keep your design looking brand new, please follow these guidelines:</p><p>Hand wash only\u00a0\ud83e\uddfc</p><p>Do not soak or use abrasive sponges.</p><p>Not\u00a0microwave or dishwasher safe \ud83d\udeab</p><br><p>The Fine Print:</p><p>Application:\u00a0Please follow the included instructions carefully. We are not responsible for damage resulting from improper application.</p><p>Returns:\u00a0Due to the nature of this product, refunds, returns, or exchanges are not accepted.</p><p>Visuals:\u00a0Mock-ups are for reference only; actual colors and sizes may vary slightly due to screen settings. (Cup not included).</p><p>Artwork:\u00a0We do not claim ownership of licensed or character images. Your purchase covers design preparation, resizing, and high-quality print production.</p>",
