        "id": 9910217638200,
        "title": "Add A Tap Quick On - Female",
        "handle": "add-a-tap-quick-on-female",
        "body_html": "<p><strong>Add a tap quick on</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Add-a-tap, quick-on</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Description</strong>:<br>Cooper 2609BK-BU Connector In-Line Single 10A 125V 2P2W Non-Polarized Black</p>\n<p><strong>Technical Description</strong>:<br>In-Line Outlet Type; Thermoplastic Material; Black Color; NEMA 1-15 Configuration; 2 Wire(S); UL, NOM 426 Approval; 125 VAC Voltage Rating; 10 Ampere Current Rating; 2 Pole(S); 18/2 AWG SPT-1 Cord Size; Constructional Feature Impact Resistant</p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<table style=\"height: 537px;\" width=\"95%\" cellspacing=\"0\" bgcolor=\"#fff\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 16px; width: 6.65143%;\" width=\"20%\"><strong>Brand Name:</strong></td>\n<td style=\"height: 16px; width: 93.2826%;\">\u00a0Eaton</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 32px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 32px; width: 6.65143%;\" width=\"20%\"><strong>Special Features:</strong></td>\n<td style=\"height: 32px; width: 93.2826%;\">\u00a0Academy plugs &amp; recepts</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 16px; width: 6.65143%;\" width=\"20%\"><strong>Sub Brand:</strong></td>\n<td style=\"height: 16px; width: 93.2826%;\">\u00a0Eaton Wiring Devices</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 16px; width: 6.65143%;\" width=\"20%\"><strong>Type:</strong></td>\n<td style=\"height: 16px; width: 93.2826%;\">\u00a0Residential</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 80px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 80px; width: 6.65143%;\" width=\"20%\"><strong>CATALOG DESCRIPTION:</strong></td>\n<td style=\"height: 80px; width: 93.2826%;\">\u00a0EATON STRAIGHT BLADE CONNECTOR , #18-10 AWG, 10A, RESIDENTIAL, 125V, BACK WIRE, BLACK, BRASS, THERMOPLASTIC, 1-15R, TWO-POLE, TWO-WIRE, NON GROUNDING, INSULATION PIERCING, 18-2 SPT-1 CORD, THERMOPLASTIC, BULK</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 41px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 41px; width: 6.65143%;\" width=\"20%\"><strong>Category:</strong></td>\n<td style=\"height: 41px; width: 93.2826%;\">\u00a0Consumer Packaged Wiring Devices</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 16px; width: 6.65143%;\">\u00a0</td>\n<td style=\"height: 16px; width: 93.2826%;\">\u00a0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 112px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 112px; width: 6.65143%;\" width=\"20%\">\u00a0</td>\n<td style=\"height: 112px; width: 93.2826%;\">\u00a0In-Line Outlet Type; Thermoplastic Material; Black Color; NEMA 1-15 Configuration; 2 Wire(S); UL, NOM 426 Approval; 125 VAC Voltage Rating; 10 Ampere Current Rating; 2 Pole(S); 18/2 AWG SPT-1 Cord Size; Constructional Feature Impact Resistant; Size 1.09 Inch W X 0.78 Inch D X 0.44 Inch H; Grounding Type Non-Grounding; Packaging Type Bulk</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 16px; width: 6.65143%;\" width=\"20%\"><strong>Manufacturer:</strong></td>\n<td style=\"height: 16px; width: 93.2826%;\">\u00a0Eaton Cooper Wiring</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 32px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 32px; width: 6.65143%;\" width=\"20%\"><strong>Manufacturer Brand:</strong></td>\n<td style=\"height: 32px; width: 93.2826%;\">\u00a0Eaton Wiring Devices Residential/Industrial</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 16px; width: 6.65143%;\">\u00a0</td>\n<td style=\"height: 16px; width: 93.2826%;\">\u00a0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 32px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 32px; width: 6.65143%;\" width=\"20%\"><strong>Product Description:</strong></td>\n<td style=\"height: 32px; width: 93.2826%;\">\u00a0Cooper 2609BK-BU Connector In-Line Single 10A 125V 2P2W Non-Polarized Black</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 16px; width: 6.65143%;\" width=\"20%\"><strong>Sub-Category:</strong></td>\n<td style=\"height: 16px; width: 93.2826%;\">\u00a0Straight Blade Low Power Outlet</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 16px; width: 6.65143%;\" width=\"20%\"><strong>UNSPSC:</strong></td>\n<td style=\"height: 16px; width: 93.2826%;\">\u0