    "https://www.lightandlilac.com": {
      "product": {
        "id": 8654492074152,
        "title": "Purple & Silver Floral Place Cards",
        "handle": "purple-silver-floral-place-cards",
        "body_html": "<p data-mce-fragment=\"1\">Real pressed flowers encased in a double sheet of acrylic, with a custom name and a silver lining.</p>\n<ul data-mce-fragment=\"1\">\n<li data-mce-fragment=\"1\">Measures approximately 2\" W x\u00a0 3.5\" H x 3/16\u201d D.</li>\n<li data-mce-fragment=\"1\">Ships from Southern California.</li>\n<li data-mce-fragment=\"1\">Since all flowers are real and unique, no two place cards will be 100% identical.</li>\n<li data-mce-fragment=\"1\">Indicate what name(s) you\u2019d like on your place card(s).</li>\n<li data-mce-fragment=\"1\">Maximum character limit: 11</li>\n<li data-mce-fragment=\"1\">Acceptable variations: Jacqueline, John S., or J. Smith.</li>\n<li data-mce-fragment=\"1\">All lettering is white vinyl and the same font as shown in listing photos.</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-mce-fragment=\"1\"><strong data-mce-fragment=\"1\">BULK DISCOUNT:</strong><br data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></p>\n<p data-mce-fragment=\"1\"><span data-mce-fragment=\"1\">1-24 cards: $9.99 per card</span><br data-mce-fragment=\"1\"><span data-mce-fragment=\"1\">25-49 cards: $9.49 per card</span><br data-mce-fragment=\"1\"><span data-mce-fragment=\"1\">50-99 cards: $8.99 per card</span><br data-mce-fragment=\"1\"><span data-mce-fragment=\"1\">100+ cards: $8.49 per card</span></p>\n<p data-mce-fragment=\"1\"><strong data-mce-fragment=\"1\"><span data-mce-fragment=\"1\" mce-data-marked=\"1\">Discount applied automatically upon checkout. If you have any trouble, don't hesitate to reach out at <meta charset=\"utf-8\">hello@lightandlilac.com</span></strong></p>\n<p data-mce-fragment=\"1\"><strong data-mce-fragment=\"1\">ADD-ONS:</strong></p>\n<p data-mce-fragment=\"1\">Adding a table number or meal preference to the cards incurs a $0.50 fee per add-on. If you'd like no lettering, there is a $1 discount per card. Contact us for the no-lettering discount: hello@lightandlilac.com</p>\n<p><br></p>",
