    "https://www.editionnaam.com": {
      "product": {
        "id": 9618649614,
        "title": "Know Thyself as Soul Magazine SINGLE ISSUES - English",
        "handle": "know-thyself-as-soul-magazine-past-issues",
        "body_html": "<p>High-quality printed copies of\u00a0single issues (English version) are available.<!-- for $2 USD each.&nbsp; Issue 4 of each year has a special price of only $1 USD. &nbsp;--></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Click on the pull-down menu above to select the issue you want to purchase.</li>\n<li>Click on the issue you want.</li>\n<li>In the \"Quantity\" box, enter how many copies of that issue you want.</li>\n<li>Click \"Add to cart.\"</li>\n<li>Repeat for any other issues that you want.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If an issue has sold out, it will\u00a0not appear in the pull-down above.\u00a0\u00a0</p>\n<p>You can also purchase <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">all of the available</span> past issues (listed in the pull-down menu) as a set (1 of each available issue) for a special price of $40 USD.\u00a0 To purchase the set, choose \"All Available Issues\" from the pull-down menu. In the \"Quantity\" box, enter how many sets you want (each set has 1 each of the issues listed in the pull-down menu; if you order 2 sets, you will receive 2 of each issue; etc.).\u00a0\u00a0</p>\n<p>If you are interested in purchasing 5 or more per issue, please <a title=\"Contact\" href=\"https://www.editionnaam.com/pages/contact\" target=\"_blank\">click here</a> to contact us about a wholesale discount.\u00a0</p>\n<p>To subscribe to the magazine, <a title=\"Subscribe KT\" href=\"https://www.editionnaam.com/collections/know-thyself-as-soul-magazine/products/know-thyself-as-soul-magazine-subscription\" target=\"_blank\">click here</a>.<br></p>\n<p>For issues in Spanish, <a title=\"Issues in Spanish\" href=\"https://www.editionnaam.com/collections/know-thyself-as-soul-magazine/products/know-thyself-as-soul-magazine-single-issues-spanish\">click here</a>.</p>",
        "published_at": "2025-03-13T00:55:59-04:00",
        "created_at": "2017-01-31T13:47:47-05:00",
        "updated_at": "2026-04-02T14:14:14-04:00",
