    "https://jemsluxefibers.com": {
      "product": {
        "id": 7830105161789,
        "title": "Kunzite",
        "handle": "kunzite-3",
        "body_html": "<div class=\"woocommerce-product-details__description\">\n<div class=\"woocommerce-product-details__short-description\">\n<p>65% Fine Superwash Merino Wool 21.5 mic,<br>35% Bamboo</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"summary__weight-and-ply-container\"><span>Fingering / Sock</span></div>\n<div class=\"summary__weight-and-ply-container\"><span>437yds/100g</span></div>\n<div class=\"summary__weight-and-ply-container\"><span>3ply</span></div>\n<p><br>Milled from a blend of superwash wool and viscose made from bamboo, Zen Luxe\u00a0will surprise and delight everyone. At first glance, the yarn displays a beautiful luster and drape reminiscent of silk, but delve a little deeper and you will find you can thank budget friendly viscose made from bamboo for the subtle sparkle! This wonderful yarn\u00a0was made with garments in mind, think elegant tops and sweaters you\u2019ll love wearing.\u00a0</p>\n</div>",
        "published_at": "2026-03-26T12:00:46-05:00",
