    "https://www.captainschocolate.com": {
      "product": {
        "id": 7682210168999,
        "title": "Organic Salted Caramel Dark Chocolate Bar (40g)",
        "handle": "organic-salted-caramel-dark-chocolate-bar-40g",
        "body_html": "<p>Experience the ultimate taste sensation with our exquisite Organic Salted Caramel Flavored Chocolate Bar. Crafted with love and care, this delightful treat features the finest organic ingredients, combining rich chocolate, creamy caramel flavor, and pure sea salt. Each delectable bite takes your taste buds on a journey of pure bliss.</p>\n<p>With a perfect balance of sweetness and a hint of sea salt, this luxurious chocolate bar is a symphony of flavors that will leave you craving for more. Treat yourself or surprise a loved one with this delectable delight - perfect for any occasion.</p>\n<p>Embrace guilt-free indulgence - order our Organic Salted Caramel Flavored Chocolate Bar and savor a moment of pure pleasure.</p>\n<p><em>Available in<strong><span>\u00a0</span>60% only.</strong>\u00a0Not sure which percentage is right for you?<span>\u00a0</span><a href=\"https://www.captainschocolate.com/pages/cacao-percentages\" title=\"understanding cacao percentages\" target=\"_blank\">Click<span>\u00a0</span>here<span>\u00a0</span>for help.</a></em></p>",
